    respond "Example: ;ashborne 3 hp_hunter_troll"
    respond "HuntPlan catalog aliases use hp_creature_name, such as hp_krag_dweller or hp_three_toed_tegu."
    respond "Style 3 covers one weapon, two weapons, two-handed weapons, and weapon plus shield."
    respond "Style 9 uses HuntPro's complete default casting cycle, including its support and cooldown spells."
    respond "Leave the custom spell rotation at 0 unless you deliberately want to replace HuntPro's normal attack choice."
