    respond "Select Ashborne before choosing or starting a HuntPlan catalog area."
    respond "If HuntPro or stable Ashborne remains selected, HuntSuggest will launch that selected engine for normal rows."
    respond "HuntSuggest saves the selected engine for the next time it opens."
    respond "Text fallback: ;huntsuggest engine ashborne"
